data.description: Welcome to 4064 Browne Court, a modern 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhome centrally located in Conley, GA. This property boasts of space ready for you to call home. New carpet and paint, creating a fresh and inviting atmosphere. The open-concept living area is complemented by a large kitchen featuring an in-sink island, granite countertops, plenty of cabinet space, and pantry storage. The property has large windows throughout allowing for natural light at all times of the day. The large fence backyard is great for relaxing, entertaining and for fur babies to safely run around.  Located near major highways, this home is perfect for both homeowners and investors alike with no HOA, the possibilities are endless. Don't miss this opportunity to make 4064 Browne Court your next real estate move.
